summary: All three requested frontend features appear implemented: a static Customer Reviews section on Home with 6 testimonial cards, a new /pests page with a responsive grid of pests including identification/signs/prevention, and expanded Services content with an "Our Treatment Process" section plus safety/prep/aftercare/eco-friendly notes. Header and footer navigation include the new Pests page link, and routing was updated accordingly.

hallucinated_features.description: Added/changed footer attribution link behavior (dynamic appIdentifier and UTM-tracked caffeine.ai link) not requested in the BuildRequest.
hallucinated_features.reason: BuildRequest only asked to add navigation links to the new Pests page and did not request changes related to external attribution/UTM tracking or dynamic identifiers.
